Map by slappy_991

This map was inspired by 'de_subway'.. it is not an exsact remake but it has the main parts of it.

CT: Stop the terroists from taking over the subway and bombing the ticket office or main enterance.

T: Take over the subway and destroy it!

Features Working vending machines and oncoming trains!.. many vents and a underground sewer type thingy ^^

Enjoy =]
